    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it’s not just about taking a break. it's like... even if i stop performing, nothing changes. i'm still stuck in this body and this life and the world is still gonna be just as hostile. how am i supposed to find peace when there's basically no way to actually be me without it being a constant war?",
